'''Kudara no Konikishi Rizen''' (百済王利善) was a noble of the {{ill|Nara period|ja|奈良時代|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. His official Rank was {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and he held the post of {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Biography ==
In the {{ill|Empress Kōken|ja|孝謙天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}'s reign, during {{ill|Tenpyō-jingo|ja|天平神護|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (765), he was granted the Rank of {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従五位下|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the following year, {{ill|Tenpyō-jingo|ja|天平神護|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (766), he was appointed {{ill|Governor of Hida Province|ja|飛騨守|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
During the {{ill|Emperor Kōnin|ja|光仁天皇|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}'s reign, he served as {{ill|Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|ja|讃岐員外介|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (771). His promotions included {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|従五位上|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Hōki 7 (776), {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|正五位下|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in Hōki 10 (779), and {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Ten'ō|ja|天応|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1 (781). In {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2 (783), he reached the Rank of {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
He passed away on the 24th day of the 5th month in Enryaku 3 (784). At the time of his death, his official position was {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Career Timeline ==
According to the {{ill|Shoku Nihongi|ja|続日本紀|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}:
* Unknown date: {{ill|Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正六位上|1=Senior Sixth Rank|lt=Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Tenpyō-jingo 1 (765), Intercalary 10th month, 6th day: {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従五位下|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Tenpyō-jingo 2 (766), 3rd month, 26th day: Appointed {{ill|Governor of Hida Province|ja|飛騨守|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Hōki 2 (771), 7th month, 23rd day: Appointed {{ill|Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|ja|讃岐員外介|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Hōki 7 (776), 1st month, 7th day: Promoted to {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|従五位上|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Hōki 10 (779), 1st month, 23rd day: Promoted to {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|正五位下|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Ten'ō 1 (781), 4th month, 15th day: Promoted to {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. 5th month, 25th day: Appointed {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Enryaku 2 (783), 10th month, 16th day: Promoted to {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Enryaku 3 (784), 5th month, 24th day: Passed away ({{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade).
