{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[d:Q45828447]] Wikidata name: (none) [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 07:41, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} {{Infobox Kuge | Name = Kudara no Konikishi Rizen (百済王利善) | image = | image Size = | Caption = | Period = [[:en:Nara period|Nara period]] | Birth Date = Unknown | Death Date = [[:en:Enryaku|Enryaku]] 3, 5th month, 24th day (June 16, 784) | Renamed = | Alias = | Posthumous Name = | Deity Name = | Buddhist Name = | Grave = | Rank = {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従四位}}・{{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/San'i no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} | Lord = [[:en:Empress Kōken|Empress Kōken]] → [[:en:Emperor Kōnin|Emperor Kōnin]] → [[:en:Emperor Kanmu|Emperor Kanmu]] | Clan = [[:en:Kudara no Konikishi clan|Kudara no Konikishi clan]] | Parents = | Notes = }} '''Kudara no Konikishi Rizen''' (百済王利善) was a noble of the [[:en:Nara period|Nara period]]. His official Rank was {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従四位}} and he held the post of {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/San'i no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. == Biography == In the [[:en:Empress Kōken|Empress Kōken]]'s reign, during [[:en:Tenpyō-jingo|Tenpyō-jingo]] 1 (765), he was granted the Rank of {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従五位下|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従五位}}. In the following year, [[:en:Tenpyō-jingo|Tenpyō-jingo]] 2 (766), he was appointed {{ill|Governor of Hida Province|ja|飛騨守|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Governor of Hida Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 飛騨国}}. During the [[:en:Emperor Kōnin|Emperor Kōnin]]'s reign, he served as {{ill|Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|ja|讃岐員外介|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} in [[:en:Hōki|Hōki]] 2 (771). His promotions included {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|従五位上|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従五位}} in Hōki 7 (776), {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|正五位下|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正五位}} in Hōki 10 (779), and {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正五位}} in {{ill|Ten'ō|ja|天応 (日本)|1=Ten'ō|2=ja|3=天応 (日本)|qq=}}{{citation needed|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten'ō|qq=}} 1 (781). In [[:en:Enryaku|Enryaku]] 2 (783), he reached the Rank of {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従四位}}. He passed away on the 24th day of the 5th month in Enryaku 3 (784). At the time of his death, his official position was {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/San'i no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}. == Career Timeline == According to the [[:en:Shoku Nihongi|Shoku Nihongi]]: * Unknown date: {{ill|Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正六位上|1=Senior Sixth Rank|lt=Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Sixth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正六位}} * Tenpyō-jingo 1 (765), Intercalary 10th month, 6th day: {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従五位下|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従五位}} * Tenpyō-jingo 2 (766), 3rd month, 26th day: Appointed {{ill|Governor of Hida Province|ja|飛騨守|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Governor of Hida Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 飛騨国}} * Hōki 2 (771), 7th month, 23rd day: Appointed {{ill|Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|ja|讃岐員外介|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Assistant Governor of Sanuki Province|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * Hōki 7 (776), 1st month, 7th day: Promoted to {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|従五位上|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従五位}} * Hōki 10 (779), 1st month, 23rd day: Promoted to {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|正五位下|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正五位}} * Ten'ō 1 (781), 4th month, 15th day: Promoted to {{ill|Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|ja|正五位上|1=Senior Fifth Rank|lt=Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank, Upper Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正五位}}. 5th month, 25th day: Appointed {{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/San'i no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * Enryaku 2 (783), 10th month, 16th day: Promoted to {{ill|Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従四位}} * Enryaku 3 (784), 5th month, 24th day: Passed away ({{ill|San'i no Kami|ja|散位頭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/San'i no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}, Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade). == Notes == {{Reflist|qq=}} == References == * Ujitani, T. *Shoku Nihongi (Middle)*. [[:en:Kodansha|Kōdansha]] (Kōdansha Gakujutsu